Quick and dirty rstan


Pre-compiled regression models


Uses familiar syntax

Regression Example

rstanarm Version

mpg_stanlm <- stan_lm(cty ~ manufacturer + displ + cyl, data = mpg
                     ,prior = R2(location = 0.6))
summary(mpg_stanlm)
